| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4649 — Recovery Inhibition (ValenciaLeaks)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4e071420-0357-50a5-b5ef-d075630e1f01"
